node.text: Kudos to them for their tasty bowls!! 😄🙌

@kudos.sg customizable chicken bowls, these balanced bowls of vegetables, grains and protein are perfect for lunch or dinner. Choose from their best selling mains and sides or mix-and-match to find your favorite combos.

I had all four bowls from ‘PICK A BOWL’ section with tomato basil soup, mushroom soup, sweet potato fries and fries. Both the Zesty Garlic Chicken and Lemon Rosemary Chicken were my favorites of the lot, thick juicy chicken meat and well marinated, flavorful and tasty!

WhatsApp 8749 9630 to pre-order. Islandwide delivery available, delivery charges apply.

#savefnbsg #supportlocalsg #stayhomesg
